The Training Buddy
What is the "Training Buddy"?
The buddy is a updated version of the best in the market training dummy.
The oldest comes from the Kunfg Fu world, the wooden dummy. Mostly immobile and limited feedback.
The markets current comes from Century MA supplies. B.O.B.. More mobile then the wooden trainer.
Now there are more modern versions of the BOB, mostly geared for MMA, grappling dummies. 
The Training Buddy (TB) will offer users the ability to adjust arms, legs, & body positions dependant on skills being trained.
The V1 will not be directly connectable to game system, but will offer a semi static PHYGITAL Adaptive Martial Arts Training System
